                    <div class="section" id="bias_reflection">
                        <div class="section-header"><h3>EXPLORING MY OWN BIASES</h3></div>
                        <div class="section-content"><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div style="position: relative; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><div class="key-definition-box"><h4>PRE-WORK REFLECTION QUIZ</h4><div><p><b>Time: 5-10 minutes</b></p><p>Before your live session, take a moment to honestly reflect on your own thought patterns and behaviours. This self-assessment is designed to help you become more aware of potential unconscious biases that we all carry.</p><p style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px; background: #f0f4ff; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;"><b>Important:</b> This quiz is <b>private</b> and <b>non-assessed</b>. There are no right or wrong answers. The purpose is simply to bring awareness that you can carry into your live workshop session.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div class="text-content-render"><p><b>Instructions:</b></p><p>For each statement below, select the response that most honestly reflects your experience. Try not to overthink your answers – your initial reaction is often the most authentic.</p></div></div><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div class="interactive-activity-wrapper" id="bias-quiz"><h4 style="color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 20px;">Self-Reflection Statements</h4><div class="bias-statement" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 15px;">1. I naturally feel more comfortable with people who are similar to me.</p><div class="likert-options" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;"><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias1" value="agree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Agree</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias1" value="unsure" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Unsure</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias1" value="disagree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Disagree</label></div></div><div class="bias-statement" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 15px;">2. I sometimes make quick judgments about people in meetings without always questioning them.</p><div class="likert-options" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;"><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias2" value="agree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Agree</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias2" value="unsure" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Unsure</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias2" value="disagree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Disagree</label></div></div><div class="bias-statement" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 15px;">3. I tend to give more attention or opportunities to team members I connect with easily.</p><div class="likert-options" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;"><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias3" value="agree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Agree</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias3" value="unsure" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Unsure</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias3" value="disagree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Disagree</label></div></div><div class="bias-statement" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 15px;">4. I notice I sometimes interrupt certain people more than others.</p><div class="likert-options" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;"><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias4" value="agree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Agree</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias4" value="unsure" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Unsure</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias4" value="disagree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Disagree</label></div></div><div class="bias-statement" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 15px;">5. When I first meet someone, their appearance influences my initial expectations of their abilities.</p><div class="likert-options" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;"><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias5" value="agree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Agree</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias5" value="unsure" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Unsure</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias5" value="disagree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Disagree</label></div></div><div class="bias-statement" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 15px;">6. I find it easier to trust information that confirms what I already believe.</p><div class="likert-options" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;"><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias6" value="agree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Agree</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias6" value="unsure" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Unsure</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias6" value="disagree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Disagree</label></div></div><div class="bias-statement" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 15px;">7. I sometimes assume I know what someone is going to say before they finish speaking.</p><div class="likert-options" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;"><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias7" value="agree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Agree</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias7" value="unsure" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Unsure</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias7" value="disagree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Disagree</label></div></div><div class="bias-statement" style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><p style="font-weight: 600; color: #2b3d6d; margin-bottom: 15px;">8. I may unintentionally favour people who have a similar background or career path to mine.</p><div class="likert-options" style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;"><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias8" value="agree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Agree</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias8" value="unsure" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Unsure</label><label style="display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;"><input type="radio" name="bias8" value="disagree" style="margin-right: 8px;"> Disagree</label></div></div></div></div><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div class="feedback-box-render"><h4>Personal Insights</h4><p>Based on your responses above, take a moment to record 1-2 personal insights. What patterns did you notice? What surprised you?</p><p style="font-style: italic; color: #666; margin-top: 10px;">Remember: Recognising our biases is the first step toward addressing them. Everyone has unconscious biases – the goal is to become aware of them so we can make more intentional decisions.</p><textarea placeholder="Write 1-2 personal insights here...

For example:
- I noticed that I tend to...
- I was surprised to realise that...
- One pattern I want to be more aware of is..."></textarea></div></div><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div style="position: relative; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><div class="key-definition-box"><h4>WHAT HAPPENS NEXT?</h4><div><p>Your reflections from this quiz are <b>for your eyes only</b>. They will not be shared or assessed.</p><p style="margin-top: 10px;">The purpose of this exercise is to bring self-awareness into your live workshop session, where you will:</p><ul style="margin-top: 10px;"><li>Explore different types of unconscious bias in more depth</li><li>Learn practical strategies for interrupting bias in your decision-making</li><li>Discuss real workplace scenarios with your peers</li><li>Develop an action plan for inclusive leadership</li></ul><p style="margin-top: 15px;"><b>Well done for completing this honest self-reflection!</b></p></div></div></div></div></div>
