                        <div class="section-header"><h3>POST-MODULE KNOWLEDGE CHECK</h3></div>
                        <div class="section-content-wrapper"><div style="position: relative; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><div class="key-definition-box"><h4>TEST YOUR UNDERSTANDING</h4><div><p>Now that you've completed this module on Inclusive Leadership in Action, let's check your understanding of the key concepts. This quiz covers DEI definitions, types of unconscious bias, inclusive leadership behaviours, and the connection between inclusion, culture, and sustainability.</p><p style="margin-top: 15px;"><b>Answer all questions to test your knowledge. You'll receive immediate feedback on each answer.</b></p></div></div></div></div>
